name: Negative flows for Credit Card Application and user journeys

steps.name: the user opens the application
the user registers with an existing email
the system should show an email already exists error
the user opens the application
a registered user exists
the user logs in with an incorrect password
the system should show 'Login was unsuccessful'
the user opens the application

elements.name: Checkout with invalid credit card number

steps.name: a product is in the cart
the user attempts payment with an invalid card number
the payment should be rejected and an error shown

embeddings.name: Checkout with invalid credit card number

name: Positive flows for Credit Card Application and user journeys

steps.name: the user opens the application
the user registers with valid details
registration should be successful
the user opens the application
a registered user exists
the user logs in with valid credentials
login should succeed
the user opens the application

elements.name: Successful credit card payment at checkout

steps.name: a product is in the cart
the user proceeds to checkout and applies a valid credit card
payment should be processed and order confirmed

embeddings.name: Successful credit card payment at checkout

steps.name: the user opens the application

elements.name: Login and add desktop product to cart

steps.name: I click login option in the home page
I should navigate to the login page
I enter user name and password
I click login button
I should navigate to the product page
I click desktop under computers menu
I select any desktop under desktop page
I should see the message as "Build your own computer" title and price
I click on add cart option
I see the message as "The product has been added"
I click shopping cart option
I see the message as "Shopping cart" page title

embeddings.name: Login and add desktop product to cart
